[[File:HamHam falls sylhet.jpg|thumb|Hum Hum Waterfall]]  
'''Hum Hum''' is a waterfall in [[Moulvibazar]], [[Bangladesh]]. It was discovered in 2010. It is situated in Razkandi reserve forest, Maulvibazar district, Sylhet.

The height of the fall is about 147 to 160 feet.

