'''Parc Central''' is a park in [[Andorra la Vella]], [[Andorra]]. It was designed by the architect [[Daniel Gelabert Fontova]].<ref name="CerverOussedik1995">{{cite book|last1=Cerver|first1=Francisco Asensio|last2=Oussedik|first2=Sylvia|last3=Huet|first3=Bernard|title=Elements of landscape|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5IBUAAAAMAAJ|accessdate=2 December 2011|year=1995|publisher=Arco Editorial Board|isbn=978-84-8185-002-4|pages=89–92}}</ref>

