'''Sebago to the Sea Trail''' is a trail that goes from [[Lake Sebago]] to the [[Gulf of Maine]]. It was created in 2007 in order to create an eventual 28 mile trail to the sea. The trail runs through the towns of [[Falmouth, Maine|Falmouth]], [[Windham, Maine|Windham]], [[Standish, Maine|Standish]], and [[Gorham, Maine|Gorham]].
